    "description": "<strong>莫提亚，这个名字曾是矮人王国的荣耀，这里诞生了无数传奇的工匠大师。然而，矮人们总是不知道何时应该停止挖掘。莫提亚的矮人在矿井深处挖掘到了某些不应被唤醒的东西。莫提亚因此沉没在了那无底的黑暗之中，永世不见天日。 神器行者新DLC《莫提亚的遗产》即将到来！新角色、新地图、新BOSS、新共鸣、新神器、新奇遇，更多新内容等着大家探索！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065220/extras/e1a8573f82dfda0da9ebaf6680cf6a04.webp?t=1721980447\" width=620 height=56 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065220/extras/9872d09ea9da7d2e0d60ba58f681ad6e.poster.avif?t=1721980447\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065220/extras/9872d09ea9da7d2e0d60ba58f681ad6e.webm?t=1721980447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065220/extras/9872d09ea9da7d2e0d60ba58f681ad6e.mp4?t=1721980447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>塞拉蒂尔，这个名字在矮人语中意味着“战斗人偶”。她是莫提亚矿洞中最后被发现的远古神器，由一个早已灭亡的古老王国的最伟大的魔法工匠精心制作。塞拉蒂尔的外表精美绝伦，坚不可摧，她的内部结构蕴含着失传的魔法和技术。她的拳套不仅是武器，更是她与世界互动的媒介，能够操纵元素力量和古代符文的魔法。尽管塞拉蒂尔拥有着几乎不可能的可爱外观，但她的真实目的和她在莫提亚灭亡中所扮演的角色仍然是一个谜。<br>特性：塞拉蒂尔不喜欢做无谓的举动，她要么不出手，要么直接将敌人秒杀。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065220/extras/812ad9db9479920094880cbf812ec5d1.avif?t=1721980447\" width=620 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065220/extras/022cb05898fd20ad07074d74fcb4d6ed.poster.avif?t=1721980447\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065220/extras/022cb05898fd20ad07074d74fcb4d6ed.webm?t=1721980447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065220/extras/022cb05898fd20ad07074d74fcb4d6ed.mp4?t=1721980447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>新角色，神器收藏家，苏拉兹<br>特性：苏拉兹的魔典会不断变换自己的形态，苏拉兹还会在战斗过程中不断地附魔成长。<br>新角色，莫提亚的幸存者，纳尔高<br>特性：矮人总是最精明和贪婪的，纳尔高总是有办法搞到最好的折扣。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065220/extras/76e22e55180fe0185b8b4576e21a53e6.webp?t=1721980447\" width=620 height=56 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065220/extras/f61cf94e7722b936fd4bb156d535a6f4.poster.avif?t=1721980447\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065220/extras/f61cf94e7722b936fd4bb156d535a6f4.webm?t=1721980447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065220/extras/f61cf94e7722b936fd4bb156d535a6f4.mp4?t=1721980447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>10+新奇遇<br>20+新神器<br>新的敌人<br>新地图<br>新boss<br>更多的新词条<br>新共鸣</strong>",
